text: Novobiryuchevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Krasnogorsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 242 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 9 km from Krasnaya Gorka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Novobiryuchevo
